    <stitle>POWER STEERING GEAR: TRW/ROSS-TAS 40, 55, 65 AND 85 - LUBRICATION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl0500301" svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>LUBRICATION</title>
        <revst/>
        <para>Refer to GROUP 10 - LUBRICATION in the CTS-5000 Master Service Manual for the type of lubrication fluid to
            use.
        </para>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Do not mix oil types. Any mixture or any unapproved oil could lead to seal deterioration and
                    leaks. A leak could ultimately cause the loss of fluid, which could result in a loss of power
                    steering assist.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <revend/>
    </svcproc>
